Class ModelRepository<T extends Model>

java.lang.Object
  com.strongloop.android.remoting.Repository
      com.strongloop.android.loopback.ModelRepository<T>

public class ModelRepository<T extends Model>
extends Repository

A local representative of a single model type on the server, encapsulating the name of the model type for easy Model creation, discovery, and management.
